&lt;li&gt;Positions TNC as a central community hub through collaborative partnerships with schools, nonprofits, civic organizations, and community stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Builds organizational alignment through communication, transparency, and collaboration across all programs and departments.&lt;/li&gt;
